data.description: MAJOR RATE BUYDOWN... 3% OFF first year. Ask about this. This generous floor plan built by Alturas boasts THREE FULL BATHS! Welcome to the highly sought after master planned Arbor community featuring modern farmhouse and urban style trends in one of the Treasure Valley’s fastest growing areas just minutes from the Treasure Valley Marketplace. Comfort and convenience combined with style from arched, coffered ceilings in the great room and master bedroom, a large shower and walk-in closet, and low maintenance yard. Floor plan provides ample and convenient living with 3 full bathrooms, 4 bedrooms, and an island-mounted sink. The oversized 2-car garage is spacious providing ample room for additional storage. Located close to Canyon County’s largest shopping and medical services and within walking distance of the nearby elementary and middle schools! It doesn't get much better than this.
